  "text": [
    "than we do",
    "when it\u2019s all",
    "wound down.",
    "I don\u2019t know",
    "why we settle",
    "to the sound.",
    "Somehow",
    "the regular",
    "click and chime",
    "of passing time,",
    "like water, turns",
    "a water wheel",
    "that turns a gear",
    "that turns a stone",
    "that turns upon",
    "another stone",
    "and fine",
    "and finer in between",
    "our dreams like grain",
    "are ground."
  ],
  "title": "We Tend to Sleep Better When the Clock Is Wound",
  "year": ""
}